    "Further, if evaluation datasets depend heavily upon \"sample\" questions for a given assessment, the question set (and thus results) may not reflect the depth and distribution of topics within an actual instance of the respective exam 44.",
    "Therefore, further benchmarks should be used to assess GPT-4 performance outside of the standardized examination context.",
    "In this study, we assess the capability of GPT-4 to answer questions from nine graduate-level final examinations for scientific trainees in the biomedical sciences.",
    "In this field, academic courses required for training toward a Doctor of Philosophy (Ph.D.) degree typically involve free-response questions requiring both background knowledge and critical thinking skills.",
    "Therefore, we expect these examinations to provide a strong benchmark of GPT-4's ability to provide correct and logically consistent responses to expert-level questions."
